text:
I have bought and sold several items on Vestiaire Collective, and I have always encountered issues, but they were somehow solved along the way. However the last time I tried relisting an item the function did not work. So I tried contacting customer support for help.
1- Chat function does not work any longer and it says there are no customer support agents available;
2- the customer support email does not exist anymore;
3- the forms to submit queries are not available either;
4- as far as I aware there was never a phone number available in Europe.
Summarizing, there is no customer support should you encounter any difficulties (and trust me, you will!). Therefore, I would rather sell on eBay or even on your own. They are not worth the fees they charge as they offer zero protection. I will sadly delete the app.
Stay away to avoid headaches!
